### Mock Network Requests at Page Level in Playwright Test

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/network.md

Shows how to block specific image requests using page-level route configuration. This method applies network mocking only to a single page instance, useful for test-specific network behavior.

```javascript
import { test, expect } from '@playwright/test';

test('loads page without images', async ({ page }) => {
  // Block png and jpeg images.
  await page.route(/(png|jpeg)$/, route => route.abort());

  await page.goto('https://playwright.dev');
  // ... test goes here
});
```

